't know what you were fighting against. Your left side was seriously injured. It was really dangerous at that time. " Wait, left shoulder? Rhode was stunned. He immediately remembered that in the end of his battle with the Void Dragon, wasn't his left side attacked? But that was his character in the game who was injured." It shouldn't have anything to do with the players themselves, right? But now, the one who was injured was himself? Although the situation before him was chaotic, Rhode quickly calmed down. This was the psychological quality of a top-tier player and the world's strongest guild leader. From the conversation with the blonde girl, Rhode learned about his current situation. He was heavily injured and collapsed in Paphield Plains." My name is Lize Noelu. I'm a member of the Star Moon Mercenary Group. I'm a Cleric. You can call me Lize. " The blonde girl introduced herself to Rhode. Rhode was in a bad state at first, but his recovery rate was pretty good. " My name is Rhode Alant. " Even though he couldn't sort out the situation, Rhode hesitated for a moment before reporting his identity and ID. " I'm from the Eastern Plains. I'm an adventurer. "" But what exactly are you fighting against? " " Why are you so heavily injured? " " I remember that there shouldn't be any particularly terrifying monsters in this plain area. " Rhode smiled awkwardly. What could he say? Could he tell Lize that he was injured in the battle with the Void Dragon, one of the Five Creator Dragons? " I understand. " Although Rhode didn't explain in detail, Lize nodded as if she understood something. After carefully examining Rhode's wound, she stood up. " I haven't eaten for two days. I'm sure you must be hungry. Please wait a moment. "" Ah, by the way, I have to report this to the leader. I think he will come to see you soon. " After saying this, the young lady nodded politely at Rhode and walked out of the room.
